OpenSim 3.0 Doxygen Documentation

The table below represents the conceptual heirarchy of OpenSim within SimTK. Each box represents a class utilized by the OpenSim API, and is built on top of (i.e., requires) the components underneath. For example, you can click on the "Model Component" block to see a list of model components, such as body, constraint, or joint.

Click on any of the boxes to navigate to corresponding class description.
